main event: A civilian observed a golden object traveling at high speed in Memphis, Tennessee on June 19, 1958.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be flying at an altitude of 10,000 to 20,000 feet,It traveled in a north to south direction,The sighting lasted approximately one minute,Only a DC-7 aircraft was reported in the area at the time,The conclusion regarding the object's nature was marked as insufficient data for evaluation.
